'''Asif n Dṛɛa''' (s [[Tutlayt Taɛrabt|tɛrabt]] : وادي درعة) iga yan wasif imqqurn zɣ isaffn n tmazirt n [[Lmɣrib]], izga zɣ idrarn n [[Aṭlas mqqurn|waṭlas imqqurn]] ɣ [[Lmɣrib]] ɣ umnid n unẓul agmuḍan ar itmnagar d [[Asif n Dads|wasif n Dads]] d [[Asif n Imini|wasif n Imini]]. Izri ɣ tiniri ar tagunit ,ar itffi kullut ɣ tamnaḍt tutrimt ɣ yill aṭlasi. Ar itffi imik ɣ ugafa n tɣrmt n [[Ṭanṭan]]<ref>Gill, Victoria (13 May 2010). "BBC News - Fossil find resolves ancient extinction mystery". ''BBC Online''. British Broadcasting Corporation.</ref>. ar ittɣar ɣ ugzzum n wasif n Dṛɛa nna illan dffir tamnaḍt n Tagunit .

Ar sxddamn aman n wasif n Dṛɛa ɣ taswit n turtitin n tzdayin d turtitin timẓyanin nna illan tama n wasif.

Ar ttidirn 225.000 n ufgan ɣ wasif n Dṛɛa nna yiwḍn tajumma n 23.000 km². Iwḍ aɣzaf n wasif nig n 1200 km, d acrcur nns 24.3 mitr mukaɛɛab ɣ tsnat.

